      "TW": "**電梯正在趕來，請防守一段時間**"
    }
  },
  "** The elevator will start moving in 20 seconds. Be inside before elevator starts moving **": {
    "translation": "** 电梯将在 20 秒后开始移动。在电梯开始移动之前进入 **",
